pr_title: feat: apisix-website redesign, added asset and config files (Sub-PR1)
pr_body:
Apache APISIX website redesign (Sub-PR: 1)

This large feature addition will be done in 3 chained PRs which for easier reviews and merging. Please merge all these 3 sub PRs together, in ascending order for no breaking changes. Dependency flow is like PR3 depends on PR2, depends on PR1.

This is the first PR supposed to be merged

Link to next PR to link
PR2 : #495 

Changes:

Addition of asset files, namely images, SVGs, videos fonts etc. and config files

pr_title: feat: apisix-website redesign, add redesigned-site sections and styles (sub-pr3)
pr_body:
Apache APISIX website redesign (sub-pr 3)

This large feature addition wil be done through 3 chained PRs which for easier reviews and merging. Please merge all these 3 sub PRs together, in ascending order for no breaking changes. Dependency flow is like PR3 depends on PR2, depends on PR1.

Update: PR1, PR2 merged. This PR is ready to be merged now.

Changes:

Addition of the redesigned sections and stylesheets.

resolve #450
